event_handlers:
onSectionTileClick: inspect the clicked section’s id and/or content_group and:
- if it corresponds to an Activity.content_group (e.g., events, classes_programs, workshops_camps, seasonal_holiday), navigate to browse.html with categoryId set to that content_group;
- if it represents memberships & passes, navigate to memberships.html without additional query parameters;
- if it represents map view, navigate to map.html without additional query parameters.
